Maintainer: Peter Meissner <retep.meissner@gmail.com>
SystemRequirements: Java
Description: Provides R bindings via 'rJava' for Kafka. 
  Kafka is a event log data base to which messages can be published or read 
  from topics subscribed to. Kafka is distributed, highly scalable, provides 
  persistent event storage and is designed for high throughput.
